Package: dtrctkit
Architecture: all
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Depends: developer-dtrace (>= 5.11), mawk, coreutils (>= 5.93), bash (>= 3.1),
 cpp, lib64z1
Description: Collection of useful documented scripts for DTrace.
 The DTraceToolkit is a collection of tools written using DTrace for the
 Solaris 10[tm] OS by Sun Microsystems[tm]. Many of these scripts will also work
 on OpenSolaris.
 .
 The tools are split into several sections such as:
 .
  - Applications
  - CPU
  - Disk
  - Extra
  - File System
  - Kernel
  - Locks
  - Memory
  - Misc
  - Network
  - Processes
  - System
  - User
  - Zones
 .
 There are a total of 104 scripts included in this package.
